data.description: This 2020 home boasts a vibrant and modern design that will captivate you from the moment you step inside! Located close to shopping and the 215, this community offers access to amenities including beautiful pools and the expansive Galaxy Park, spanning nearly 10 acres with two dog parks and a playground. Upon entry, you're greeted by an open living space connected to the kitchen. The kitchen features granite countertops and a spacious island that doubles as a breakfast bar, while the large pantry ensures you'll never be short on storage space. The primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet and an oversized bathroom, offering a tranquil retreat at the end of the day. Step outside to your own private oasis, complete with pavers, turf, and an electrical retractable awning (with auto-retract functionality) providing shade during hot summer months.  PLUS all appliances to be transferred to the new owner, to include rods, blinds, & a 240-gallon GE water softener! A MUST see come view TODAY!
